Operating lease commitments — As lessee

In addition to the land use rights disclosed in Note 15, the Group and the Company entered into commercial leases on certain properties and motor vehicles. These leases have tenures range from one to five years (2016: One to five years) with no renewal option or escalation clauses included in the contracts. The Group is not restricted from subleasing the leased assets to third parties.
